248
00:17:28,958 --> 00:17:32,111
Et insultant. Et petit.

249
00:17:32,695 --> 00:17:34,313
Ok.

250
00:17:39,407 --> 00:17:41,361
Très bien.

251
00:17:44,146 --> 00:17:48,972
